## Quick Reference

`just` tool with a `justfile` in root of the repository contains useful commands for activating and managing python environment and managing common tasks

| Task | Command |
|------|---------|
| Run tests | `just test`|
| Lint code | `just lint`|
| Format code | `just format` |
| Fix lint issues | `just fix` |
| Add dependency | `uv add <package>` |
| Run demo | `just demo` |
| Clean files | `just clean` |

